msgstr "Herstellen van op Docker gebaseerde opstelling"

#: admin/backup.rst:236
msgid ""
"The following steps assume the official Docker Compose setup using the "
"bundled PostgreSQL and Valkey services, see :doc:`install/docker`. If your "
"deployment uses an external database or a customized Compose file, adapt the "
"database and volume steps to that environment."
msgstr ""
"De volgende stappen gaan uit van de officiële Docker Compose-instellingen "
