msgstr ""
"Opgeslagen in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/ssh`` en :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/home``."

#: admin/backup.rst:426
msgid ""
"If you are using SSH or GPG keys generated by Weblate, you should back up "
