"need to be backed up."
msgstr ""
"Gemaakte SSH-wrapperscripts worden opgeslagen in :setting:`CACHE_DIR` en "
"hoven niet te worden geback-upt."

#: admin/backup.rst:434
msgid "User uploaded files"
msgstr "Door gebruiker geüploade bestanden"

#: admin/backup.rst:436
msgid "Stored in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/media``."
msgstr "Opgeslagen in :setting:`DATA_DIR` ``/media``."

#: admin/backup.rst:438
msgid "You should back up all user uploaded files (e.g. :ref:`screenshots`)."
msgstr ""
"U zou alle door gebruikers geüploade bestanden moeten back-uppen "
