msgid "Avoiding merge conflicts"
msgstr "Conflicten met samenvoegen vermijden"

#: admin/continuous.rst:105
msgid ""
"The merge conflicts from Weblate arise when same file was changed both in "
"Weblate and outside it. Depending on the situation, there are several "
"approaches that might help here:"
msgstr ""
"De conflicten met samenvoegen in Weblate treden op als hetzelfde bestand "
