#: admin/install/docker.rst:2592
msgid ""
"There is `no clean way <https://github.com/docker/compose/issues/7231>`__ to "
"do this with ``docker-compose.override.yml``. You *could* add ``build: .`` "
"to the ``weblate`` node in that file, but then your custom image will be "
"tagged as ``weblate/weblate`` in your system, which could be problematic."
