"uitgave van Weblate:"

#: admin/install/source.rst:75
msgid ""
"Mismatched versions of these packages are more likely to break at runtime or "
"during tests than other Python dependency substitutions."
msgstr ""
"Niet-overeenkomende versies van deze pakketten zullen eerder defect raken in "
"runtime of gedurende testen dan andere vervangingen van afhankelijkheden van "
"Python."

#: admin/install/source.rst:80
