"In the Docker container this can be configured "
"using :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_ANON` "
"and :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_USER`."
msgstr ""
"In de Docker container kan dit worden geconfigureerd "
"met :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_ANON` "
"en :envvar:`WEBLATE_API_RATELIMIT_USER`."

