msgstr "Weblate 4.3"

#: changes/v4.rst:986
msgid "*Released on October 15th 2020.*"
msgstr "*Uitgegeven op 15 oktober 2020.*"

#: changes/v4.rst:988
msgid "Include user stats in the API."
