"browser users, API clients, project-scoped tokens, repository webhooks, VCS "
"repositories, backup archives, background workers, and configured external "
"services, then stores and synchronizes translation projects through a "
"database, datastore, local filesystem repositories, and external code-"
"hosting systems. *(documented)* (source: :doc:`/index`, :doc:`/api`, :doc:`/"
"admin/continuous`)"
