#: security/threat-model.rst:192
msgid "Project backup archives and Weblate filesystem"
msgstr "Projectback-uparchieven en Weblate bestandssysteem"

#: security/threat-model.rst:193
msgid ""
"Uploaded ZIP members and metadata become restored project state; generated "
"project backups are written to and read from local backup storage. "
"*(documented)* (source: :doc:`/admin/backup`, :doc:`/"
