#: security/threat-model.rst:292
msgid ":setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`, proxy SSL headers, and HSTS settings"
msgstr ":setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`, proxy SSL-headers en instellingen voor HSTS"

#: security/threat-model.rst:293
msgid ""
"HTTPS affects secure cookies, redirects, HSTS, WebAuthn, and generated URLs. "
"*(documented)* (source: :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`)"
msgstr ""
"HTTPS beïnvloedt beveiligde cookies, verwijzingen, HSTS, WebAuthn en "
"gegenereerde URL's. *(documented)* (source: :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:295
msgid ""
"Disabling or misconfiguring HTTPS removes transport and cookie protections "
"that Weblate relies on for browser security. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`)"
msgstr ""
"Uitschakelen of foutief configureren van HTTPS verwijdert beveiligingen voor "
"transport en cookies waarop Weblate vertrouwt voor beveiliging van de "
"browser. *(documented)* (source: :setting:`ENABLE_HTTPS`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:297
msgid ""
"The documented production posture is HTTPS with correct proxy headers. "
"*(documented)*"
msgstr ""
"De gedocumenteerde houding voor productie is HTTPS met de juiste proxy-"
"headers. *(documented)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:300
msgid ""
"Configures accepted HTTP hostnames. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ALLOWED_HOSTS`)"
msgstr ""
"Configureert geaccepteerde HTTP-hostnamen. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ALLOWED_HOSTS`"

#: security/threat-model.rst:301
msgid ""
"Broad host acceptance can weaken host-header based protections and URL "
"generation assumptions. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Breed accepteren van host kan de hostgebaseerde beveiligingen en aannames "
"voor het maken van URL's verzwakken. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:303
msgid ""
"Production deployments restrict this to instance hostnames. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Uitrollen voor productie beperken dit tot hostnamen voor de instantie. "
"*(maintainer)*"

