#: security/threat-model.rst:307
msgid ""
"Rate limits are configurable. *(documented)* (source: :doc:`/api`, :doc:`/"
"admin/config`)"
msgstr ""
"Ladinglimieten zijn te configureren. *(documented)* (source: :doc:`/"
