#: security/threat-model.rst:309
msgid ""
"Availability claims assume rate limits appropriate to deployment size and "
"exposure. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Claims voor beschikbaarheid gaan uit van ladinglimieten die toepasselijk "
"zijn voor grootte en weergave van de uitrol. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:311
msgid ""
"Disabling rate limits changes DoS triage from Weblate bug to deployment "
"posture unless a single request violates a claimed property. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Uitschakelen van ladinglimieten wijzigt DoS-triage vanuit de Weblate-bug "
"voor de houding van de uitrol, tenzij een enkel verzoek een geclaimde "
"eigenschap schendt. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:314
msgid ":setting:`CSP_SCRIPT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_IMG_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_CONNECT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_STYLE_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_FONT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_FORM_SRC`"
msgstr ":setting:`CSP_SCRIPT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_IMG_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_CONNECT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_STYLE_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_FONT_SRC`, :setting:`CSP_FORM_SRC`"

#: security/threat-model.rst:317
msgid ""
"Content Security Policy sources are configurable. *(documented)* "
"(source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"
msgstr ""
"Bronnen voor Content Security Policy zijn te configureren. *(documented)* "
"(source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:318
msgid ""
"Broadening sources can reduce browser-side containment for XSS or third-"
"party content. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Uitbreiden van de bronnen kan de beperking aan de zijde van de browser "
"verkleinen voor XSS of inhoud van derde partijen. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:320
msgid ""
"Deployments adding third-party sources accept that expanded browser trust. "
"*(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Uitrollen die bronnen van derde partijen toevoegen, accepteren dat "
"uitgebreide vertrouwen voor de browser. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:322
msgid ":setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO`"
msgstr ":setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_MEMBERS`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_TOTAL_UNCOMPRESSED_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MIN_RATIO_SIZE`, :setting:`PROJECT_BACKUP_IMPORT_MAX_COMPRESSED_ENTRY_RATIO`"

#: security/threat-model.rst:328
msgid ""
"Defaults bound project backup upload and import size, member count, and "
"suspicious compression ratios. *(documented)* (source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"
msgstr ""
"Standaard gebonden grootte voor projectback-up uploaden en importeren, "
"tellen van leden en verdachte compressieverhoudingen. *(documented)* "
"(source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:330
msgid ""
"Raising or disabling these limits expands restore-time resource exposure. "
"*(documented)* (source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"
msgstr ""
"Verhogen of uitschakelen van deze limieten vergroot het weergeven van "
"hersteltijd voor de bron. *(documented)* (source: :doc:`/admin/config`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:332
msgid ""
"The defaults documented above are part of backup-import resource guarantees. "
"*(documented)*"
msgstr ""
"De hierboven vermelde standaarden maken deel uit van de brongaranties voor "
"back-up importeren. *(documented)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:334
msgid "Private-target restrictions and allowlists for outbound URLs"
msgstr "Private-doelbeperkingen en toegestane lijsten voor uitgaande URL's"

#: security/threat-model.rst:335
msgid ""
"User-configurable outbound URL surfaces documented with private-target "
"restriction settings, including Fedora Messaging AMQP broker URLs, reject "
"internal or non-public targets by default. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`)"
msgstr ""
"Door gebruiker te configureren uitgaande URL-oppervlakken, gedocumenteerd "
"met instellingen voor beperking van private-doel, inclusief Fedora Messaging "
"AMQP tussen-URLs, weigeren standaard interne of niet-publieke doelen. "
"*(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ASSET_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`WEBHOOK_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`, :setting:`VCS_RESTRICT_PRIVATE`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:341
msgid ""
"Allowlist settings and privileged configuration can intentionally expand "
"reachability. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS`)"
msgstr ""
"Instellingen voor toegestane lijsten en geprivilegieerde configuratie kunnen "
"opzettelijk de bereikbaarheid uitbreiden. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`ASSET_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`PROJECT_WEB_RESTRICT_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`WEBHOOK_PRIVATE_ALLOWLIST`, :setting:`VCS_ALLOW_HOSTS`)"

#: security/threat-model.rst:345
msgid ""
"Default private-target rejection is an application-level security property "
"for the documented user-configurable URL surfaces. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Standaard weigeren van private-doel is een beveiligingseigenschap op "
"toepassingsniveau voor de gedocumenteerde door gebruikers te configureren "
"URL-oppervlakken. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:349
msgid ""
"Allows custom SSH options. *(documented)* (source: :setting:`SSH_EXTRA_ARGS`)"
msgstr ""
"Aangepaste opties voor SSH toestaan. *(documented)* "
"(source: :setting:`SSH_EXTRA_ARGS`"

#: security/threat-model.rst:350
msgid ""
"Weakening SSH algorithms or host verification changes VCS transport "
"assumptions. *(maintainer)*"
msgstr ""
"Verzwakken van SSH-algoritmes of hostverificatie wijzigt de aannames voor "
"VCS-transport. *(maintainer)*"

#: security/threat-model.rst:352
