msgstr ""
"`Encryptie-items niet onderworpen aan de EAR <https://www.bis.gov/learn-"
"support/encryption-controls/encryption-items-not-subject-to-ear>`_"

#: security/us-compliance.rst:49
msgid ""
"`BIS mass market guidance <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/encryption-"
"controls/mass-market>`_"
msgstr ""
"`BIS begeleiding voor grote schaal <https://www.bis.gov/learn-support/"
"encryption-controls/mass-market>`_"

