#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Internet ↔ Web server:** Public internet traffic interacting with the "
#~ "first line of defense."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**Internet ↔ Webserver:** Openbaar internetverkeer interacteert met "
#~ "eerste lijn van de verdediging."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Webhook source ↔ Web server:** External code hosting services or other "
#~ "callers invoking repository hooks, sometimes with unauthenticated "
#~ "endpoints enabled per project."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**Webhook bron ↔ Webserver:** Externe codehosting services of andere "
